data.description: "Charming three-bedroom, two-bath home in Cimarron Master Plan Community. Built in 2001, this one-story gem offers a functional floor plan with 1,784 sq ft of tasteful features. Located on a 0.19-acre lot, it boasts a spacious rear yard with RV parking and access to nearby walking trails. Enjoy the convenience of a good-sized walk-in pantry. Ideal for families, retirees, first time home buyers, investors. Situated near excellent schools. Don't miss out on this well-maintained property with a price to sell!"
